<div class="slide">
    <h1>A paradigm shift</h1>
    <h2>This is not really the end of the Web, just the end of the Web as we
        know it.</h2>

	<p class="big center">(But I feel fine.)</p>
</div>

<div class="slide">
	<h1>In context; a timeline.</h1>
	<ul class="big center">
	<li>How the Web began.</li>
	<li>How it died.</li>
	<li>What do we do now?</li>
	</ul>
</div>

<div class="slide">
	<h1>Act I</h1>
	<p class="center big">From a wonderful document delivery platform to an awful hack in less than 20
	years.</p>
</div>

